3301414@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Self-service huts naturally have a more limited choice of food.@@@@1@10@@danf@24-8-2004
3301415@unknown@formal@none@1@S@You will find mostly dried and canned dinners, and different sorts of crackers for breakfast.@@@@1@15@@danf@24-8-2004
3301416@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Bringing a bread might be an idea.@@@@1@7@@danf@24-8-2004
3301417@unknown@formal@none@1@S@What to bring?@@@@1@3@@danf@24-8-2004
