3301422@unknown@formal@none@1@S@This can be bought at DNT in Oslo, and at the different member organizations, which have offices in nearly every city in Norway.@@@@1@23@@danf@24-8-2004
3301423@unknown@formal@none@1@S@For payment it can be wise to bring both cash and a credit card.@@@@1@14@@danf@24-8-2004
3301424@unknown@formal@none@1@@Don't think twice about bringing cash, stealing is unheard of in Norwegian Mountains!@@@@0@13@@danf@24-8-2004
